nanopi
===========================================================

Scripts, configuration and other stuff for my raspberry pi.

Contents:
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- aptconf:		script configuring apt and adding apt sources
- display-stats.py:	display usage informations on tft display in Ã¼ber-fancy way
- nanopi-downloader:	download various additional stuff for raspberry pi
			x bcm2835 		(tft display module for broadcom 2835 and compatible)
			x c-berry 		(official examples for the c-berry tft display)
			x c-berry-python	(7soft python examples for the c-berry tft display)
			x c-berry-python-lib	(pixelsetzer python lib for the c-berry tft display)
			x suld			(samsung unified printer driver and cups setup)
- piconnect:		shortcut to quickly ssh-connect to my raspberry pi
- piftp:		start an ssh-ftp session in $HOME of raspberry pi user
- pipull:		grab files from raspberry pi using scp (into $PWD of computer user)
- pipush:		push files to raspberry pi using scp (into $HOME of raspberry pi user)
- purgex11:		shortcut to easily uninstall x11 to save space and resources
- raspimg:		backup the raspberry pi debian to my computer
- rfconn:		scan for bluetooth devices and pair with them
- sethost:		change raspberry pi hostname (requires restart)
- wifisetup:		set modprobe options for edimax wifi usb adapter and setup wifi network
- xinit:		additional, custom init script for raspberry pi (start obexpushd and display-stats.py)
